text: Aethiopsestis is a genus of moths belonging to the subfamily Thyatirinae of the Drepanidae. ==Species== * Aethiopsestis austrina Watson, 1965 * Aethiopsestis echinata Watson, 1965 * Aethiopsestis mufindiae Watson, 1965 ==References== Category:Thyatirinae Category:Drepanidae genera
title: Aethiopsestis
